Package: meteoclimaticR
Title: Easy access to current and historical daily meteorological data from Meteoclimatic network
Version: 0.0.2
Authors@R: c(
    person("Marc", "Lemus-Canovas", role = c("aut", "cre"), 
            email = "mlemus@ub.edu", 
            comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-0925-3827")))
Description: Get latest meteorological data (precipitation, 
    temperature, relative humidity,wind, etc.) for all the stations provided in the Meteoclimatic network (https://www.meteoclimatic.net/). Furthermore, download daily historical data since 2012 for the available weather stations.
